snippet.title: Star Stable AUTUMN RIDERS | Playthrough
snippet.description:
This is a playthrough of the first Star Stable game - Autumn Riders - that was released after the Starshine Legacy game series around 2005 for the Penny Girl book clubs. 

I didn't get to finish the game ever though unfortunately. As you can see at the end I ran into a bug and I was never able to fix it. This means I would have to start the whole game from the beginning and I don't wanna do it, this game was so annoying to play XD
